<SLUG> BC-BBA-YANKS-INDIANS-ART-1STLD-WRITETHRU-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
UNSTOPPABLE YANKS CRUSH INDIANS IN ALCS OPENER 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Subs to add art note) (ART ADV: Photos have been sent to NYT photo clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(bl) 
 By BUSTER OLNEY   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
