<HEADLINE>
GROWTH OF THE HISPANIC VOTE: A POLITICAL EARTHQUAKE IN THE MAKING 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For release Sunday, Oct. 11)   (EDs: graphics and photos available on the Wieck database.)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By STEWART M. POWELL  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
