<P>
   RABBI-PRAYER _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ The rabbi who wrote a
prayer President Clinton used did not write a sermon about him.
Rabbi Jack Riemer may be the only preacher in the country who did
not speak about the president's moral problems on Yom Kippur, the
Jewish day of atonement, last week. ``The purpose of the day is to
focus on our own sins,'' said Riemer. (Gushee, Palm Beach Post)
MOVED.
</P>
