<P>
   AIDA-REVIEW _ ATLANTA _ Theater review. World premiere of the
Elton John-Tim Rice musical ``Elaborate Lives: The Legend of
Aida,'' Wednesday night at the Alliance Theatre. 20. (Hulbert,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)ETA 8 p.m. ET. WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
