decide today whether Allied Signal has legal grounds to proceed
with the next phase of its $10 billion hostile takeover bid for
AMP. Meanwhile, AMP's efforts to block the acquisition were dealt a
blow Monday night when the Pennsylvania House approved legislation
containing conflicting language about corporate takeovers. By
Sharon R. King.
