 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    FIRING UP LATIN AMERICA: Facing shrinking markets at home, major
multinational tobacco companies are targeting Latin America for
their next generation of consumers.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-LATAM-SMOKES-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
