   MUMMY-KITTEN (Columbia, Mo.) _ For decades, scientists thought a
2,000-year-old mummified kitten from Egypt was a fake. But on a
computer screen Tuesday at the University of Missouri-Columbia, the
truth was clear: There really was a cat inside the wrappings. By
LYNN FRANEY. Story will move in ``a'' category.
