winner David Cone to the mound in search of a 2-0 lead in the
best-of-seven playoff series of the American League playoffs. By
JOSEPH DUARTE.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-NL (Atlanta) _ The Atlanta Braves play host to the San Diego
Padres in Game 1 of the National League Championship Series. By
CARLTON THOMPSON.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-OKLAHOMA (Oklahoma City) _ The Oklahoma football program,
once the pride and joy of the state, continues to hit new lows with
little hope of improvement in sight. How long will the Sooner
faithful put up with this, even with one of the school's own
running the program? By JEROME SOLOMON.
</P>
<P>
   For Sunday:
