show-and-tell class Thursday morning. ``How much did it cost?''
That was the first question posed to Patrick's dad, Jim, who, an
hour or so after visiting his son's school, phoned his Florida
Marlins employers and told them he was quitting as their manager.
(Stoda, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
