<P>
   BELL-ADAGENCY _ BellSouth has fired the ad agency that it hired
several weeks ago when it turned out that the agency also had a big
contract with Sprint. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SOCOMPANY _ Southern Co, will build a natural gas powered
electricity power plant in Wisconsin to sell electricity into
national wholesale markets. It's part of a strategy to develop
generating capacity in selected regions outside the company's
Southeastern U.S. service trerritory. (Quinn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   AUSTIN-VENTURES _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Austin Ventures, Central
Texas' largest venture capital firm, is raising another $250
million to invest in fast-growth companies in Austin and the
Southwest. The new fund will bring the total amount of money
managed by Austin Ventures to more than $700 million, making it the
largest venture capital firm in the Southwest based on amount of
money under management. (Hawkins, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
