</P>
<P>
   OUT-BOAT (Los Angeles) _ Ariane Compagnone, a graduate film
student at UCLA, is now editing footage she shot on her second
Atlantic crossing, made during the thick of the winter's El Nino
storms.
</P>
<P>
   By Jeremy Bagott. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   OUT-BIKING (Los Angeles) _ Electric bikes are popular for
commuting and recreation for seniors, but there is a controversey
brewing over ``motorized'' bikes on trails.
</P>
