<HEADLINE>
CONGRESSIONAL REPUBLICANS AGREE ON BANKRUPTCY REFORM 
</HEADLINE>
   (Eds: ADDS new 8th graf, The industry ..., with background on bill;
SUBS 8th graf pvs, Both the House ..., to UPDATE that House vote on
bill could come Thursday; minor changes elsewhere.) 
(nk)  
